{"tid":923413,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[奶閪高手]如何練成摩打脷？","createTime":"2018-12-01T08:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-01T18:03:58.000Z","uid":64601,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0531eb49bbd5870390b6b6da54b1a288c0bd2b","tid":923413,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:34:45.000Z","msg":"如果要練成一秒奶十下，首先要有條強壯嘅奶閪機器，好多人唔識點用條脷，鳩用只會控制唔到速度，就好似跑馬拉松咁，你一開始奶撚到噴射機咁，到頭嚟條脷抽筋條女都未夠喉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁究竟點練成條持久又有力嘅脷呢？首先要先要學識點發力。好多人以為要靠向上奶嚟發力，其實咁係大錯特錯，正確嚟講一定要係由上而下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解咁講？就好似昇龍拳同斷魂掌，你覺得邊個打力啲啦嗱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 初學者可以靠頂一頂上顎牙肉，條脷再向下用力彈。日子有功，你可以掂一掂上顎就可以發出如伏虎之力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n持久嚟講，你練成上面方法，再不斷重複，持續十分鐘又唔攰嘅就代表成功。如果做到自動分泌口水嘅，你嘅奶閪技術不在我之下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以奶到一口好閪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eab72daf2387e89f4d98a94a93e14e52562e723","tid":923413,"uid":64601,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T08:36:42.000Z","msg":"btw，玩過phone sex條女叫我喺電話奶出聲奶一個鐘，先知道自己原來都有極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/l